<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥- ما أَصابَ مِنْ مُصِيبَةٍ فِي الْأَرْضِ وَلا فِي أَنْفُسِكُمْ إِلَّا فِي كِتابٍ مِنْ قَبْلِ أَنْ نَبْرَأَها إِنَّ ذلِكَ عَلَى اللَّهِ يَسِيرٌ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لِكَيْلا تَأْسَوْا عَلى ما فاتَكُمْ وَلا تَفْرَحُوا بِما آتاكُمْ وَاللَّهُ لا يُحِبُّ كُلَّ مُخْتالٍ فَخُورٍ <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الَّذِينَ يَبْخَلُونَ وَيَأْمُرُونَ النَّاسَ بِالْبُخْلِ وَمَنْ يَتَوَلَّ فَإِنَّ اللَّهَ هُوَ الْغَنِيُّ الْحَمِيدُ <span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٦- وَاللَّيْلِ إِذا يَغْشى <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَالنَّهارِ إِذا تَجَلَّى <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَما خَلَقَ الذَّكَرَ وَالْأُنْثى <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِنَّ سَعْيَكُمْ لَشَتَّى <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطى وَاتَّقى <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَصَدَّقَ بِالْحُسْنى <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْيُسْرى <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَمَّا مَنْ بَخِلَ وَاسْتَغْنى <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَكَذَّبَ بِالْحُسْنى <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْعُسْرى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) الحديد: ٢٢- ٢٤ مدنية<br>(٢) الليل: ١- ١٠ مكية</p> </div>